data.description: REDUCTION! Assumable VA loan!! You will feel like you are home when you enter this beautiful custom built 4bdr/3ba property in the sought after Warrior's Path community. The kitchen is the center of activity with a walk in pantry, breakfast bar, island, and dual sinks.  It is open to both the dining area and living area to gather with family and friends.  The bonus room can be used as an office, gym, or playroom for the kiddos.  Cozy up to the wood-burning fireplace in the living area, with plenty of room for guests over for movie night or football games.  The master bedroom has a recessed ceiling and large windows to allow the morning sun to start your day.  The spacious master bath boasts a separate shower with a rain head spray and bench seating, dual vanities, and a garden tub for relaxing after a long day.  Entertain guests on the extended deck off of the covered patio with several mature trees to shade the yard.  Enjoy watching Koi swim in the custom built pond with front viewing glass. Solar panels installed on the roof allow you to save thousands of dollars per year in energy expense during the long Texas summers.  All conveniently located near grocery stores, restaurants, pharmacies, schools, coffee shops and Market Heights Shopping Plaza.  You owe it to yourself to see this charming home today!
